Perfect for traveling couples who prefer a more private setting and yet happy to meet other fellow travelers.

Each bunk bed is fitted with new 8 inch spring mattress, international power points, shelf, night lamp and a large locker.

The space
Housed in a chirpy art deco heritage building, Beary Best! was conceived with the simple intent to merge backpackers practicality with hotel like facilities and comfort.

With 3 large floor space, the building features a large lounge area for interactions with other travelers, airy dorms and hallways, pantry area and even a little outdoor patio.

Our building is located just 1 minute away from the Chinatown MRT Exit E & F.

Guest access
* Free Coffee and Tea all day
* Free WiFi internet access and use of netbooks
* Free local phone calls
* NO CURFEW – 24 hour Reception Service (Late check-ins at NO Extra Charges)
* Free same day storage after checkout<

name: 2 bedroom condo, high floor
description:
New condominium close to the river front. Enjoy views of the estate from the top floor. Close to the LRT station and well connected to major highways and the airport. Quick walk to a popular mall.

The space
It is a cozy and comfortable 2-bedroom apartment with 2 bathrooms, a queen-sized bed plus a single-sized bed. We have an extra mattress on request for the fourth guest. Enjoy views of the estate through the floor-to-ceiling glass windows.

Guest access
We stay with our parents most of the time, so guests can feel free to share our entire home during their stay.

Other things to note
Guests may do light cooking in the kitchen. The kitchen is equipped with a small gas burner, a small electric heating hob, an oven, a microwave oven, a fridge, basic kitchenware and utensils.

Washing machine, detergent and laundry rack is provided for guests.

A quaint little street just minutes away from Orchard Road, it serves as an interesting glimpse into Singapore's history right in the middle of the city’s largest shopping district.

A quaint little street just minutes away from Orchard Road, it serves as an interesting glimpse into Singapore's history right in the middle of the city’s largest shopping district.

The space
The humble abode maintains its historic Peranakan flavour with its cool green exterior, while holding true to a classic elegance throughout its interior. Newly renovated on March 2018, the impeccably clean and spacious room features a Queen Sized bed, a work table, fresh linens, towels and toiletries, all fully provided for. name: Marina Bay 2BR w/ pool & tennis, nr Downtown mrt
description:
Show up and start living from day one in Singapore with this bright two-bedroom Blueground apartment. You’ll love coming home to this thoughtfully furnished, beautifully designed, and fully-equipped Marina Bay home with stunning high floor views over the city. (ID #SGP5)

The space
As with any Blueground apartment, you’ll find a thoughtfully designed space complete with beautiful furniture and a fully-equipped kitchen in this two-bedroom property. And, thanks to our superior quality mattresses, luxury linens, and towels, you can relax knowing you’ll always feel comfortably at home. When you’re ready for some fun, you can take in the Singapore vibes or bring the entertainment to you with the premium wireless speaker or smart TV. This apartment also offers in-apartment laundry.

Amenities

Building amenities unique to this two-bedroom include an on-site:

- BBQ Area
- Doorman
- Dryer
- Elevator
- Game room
